(411, 1, '2018-01-17 11:52:02', '2018-01-17 06:22:02', 'Wowza is such a wonderful live streaming engine with Video-On-Demand(VOD) feature. It has much more add-on features introduced in recent versions like nDVR, Transcoder, DRM etc. You can even use Stream Targets option in Wowza Streaming Engine Manager for simulcast your stream to social media like facebook, youtube, Akamai etc. In this short post, I will only describe that how you can setup <b>Wowza Stream Targets</b> for facebook and youtube.\r\n<h2>Facebook</h2>\r\nSetup Facebook as a stream target is very easy because Wowza Streaming Engine Manager handles log in to Facebook to authorize your account as a Facebook Live stream target itself. Please follow the simple steps displayed in the following video:\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZRWTnmHof_g\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r\n<h2>Youtube</h2>\r\nSetup youtube as a stream target is little tricky. I have spent almost four hours and got the steps. Actually, Wowza Streaming Engine Manager does not authorize your youtube account itself. You need to get your <b>Stream Name/Key</b> from youtube <b>Creator Studio</b> yourself. Please see the following video that will help you:\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9AYCwibnjDE?rel=0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<b>IMPORTANT:</b>\r\n\r\nYou must need to verify your mobile number to get the <b>Stream Name/Key</b> from youtube. After verifing the mobile number click on <b>LIVE STREAMING</b> on the left sidebar. At the end of the page you will get the <b>Stream Name/Key</b>\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_413\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"593\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-413\" src=\"http://trickntip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/youtube-stream-name-key.jpeg\" alt=\"youtube stream name key\" width=\"593\" height=\"224\" /> youtube stream name key[/caption]\r\n\r\nThere are many other target destinations in Wowza Streaming Engine Manager, Please see the following:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_412\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"727\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-412\" src=\"http://trickntip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/wowza-stream-targets.jpeg\" alt=\"Setup Wowza Stream Targets\" width=\"727\" height=\"795\" /> Setup Wowza Stream Targets[/caption]\r\n<h2>For Developers</h2>\r\nYou can also setup Wowza Stream Targets using REST API <a href=\"https://github.com/WowzaMediaSystems/wse-rest-library-php\" target=\"_BLANK\">Wowza SDK</a>.\r\nI have just posted this article in a great hurry to save your time when setup Wowza Stream Targets from Wowza Streaming Engine Manager. Right now, I am working on <a href=\"https://github.com/WowzaMediaSystems/wse-rest-library-php\" target=\"_BLANK\">Wowza SDK</a> with Cake PHP 3.x. If you have any questions, please ask in the comment below.', 'Setup Wowza Stream Targets', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'setup-wowza-stream-targets', '', '', '2018-01-17 12:26:10', '2018-01-17 06:56:10', '', 0, 'http://trickntip.com/?p=411', 0, 'post', '', 1),
