(418, 1, '2018-01-18 11:09:46', '2018-01-18 05:39:46', 'This is a very common error by Wowza Streaming Engine Manager that your IP address blocked. Actually, when we install Wowza Streaming Engine, by default it only allows 127.0.0.1 IP. To send the streaming from mobile devices or using some other utility you have to allow those all IP address. Even if you are a programmer and you are using REST API to connect to your Wowza Streaming Engine then you have to allow your IP address. I have also experienced the same error and successfully resolved the error.\r\n\r\nThis is how my problem looks like:\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_419\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"486\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-419\" src=\"http://trickntip.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ip-address-blocked-wowza.jpeg\" alt=\"IP Address Blocked in Wowza\" width=\"486\" height=\"382\" /> IP Address Blocked in Wowza[/caption]\r\n\r\nIf you are using REST API then you will see following error\r\n<pre> stdClass Object\r\n    (\r\n        [message] =&gt; Your IP address (201.163.46.154) has been blocked\r\n        [wowzaServer] =&gt; 4.7.3\r\n        [success] =&gt; \r\n        [code] =&gt; 403\r\n    )\r\n</pre>\r\n<h2>Solution</h2>\r\nI have installed Wowza Streaming Engine 4.7.3 on Centos server. Just go to your directory where Wowza is installed and make changes in <code>conf/Server.xml</code> file. Search for a line: <code>&lt;IPWhiteList&gt;127.0.0.1&lt;/IPWhiteList&gt;</code> and replace with <code>&lt;IPWhiteList&gt;*&lt;/IPWhiteList&gt;</code> or if you want to allow your specific IP address then use a comma(,) to sperate the IPs like <code>&lt;IPWhiteList&gt;127.0.0.1,201.163.46.154&lt;/IPWhiteList&gt;</code>.\r\n\r\nThe last important step is to restart your Wowza Streaming Engine with the following command:\r\n<pre>	service WowzaStreamingEngine restart\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mEnYMNJ99GA\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 'IP Address Blocked in Wowza', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ip-address-blocked-wowza', '', '', '2018-01-18 11:49:05', '2018-01-18 06:19:05', '', 0, 'http://trickntip.com/?p=418', 0, 'post', '', 0),
